jbt.model.task.decorator
Class ModelLimit

java.lang.Object
  jbt.model.core.ModelTask
      jbt.model.task.decorator.ModelDecorator
          jbt.model.task.decorator.ModelLimit

public class ModelLimit
extends ModelDecorator

Limit is a decorator that limits the number of times a task can be executed. This decorator is used when a task (the child of the decorator) must be run a maximum number of times. When the maximum number of times is exceeded, the decorator will fail forever on.
